{
  "stem": "24268.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then also with my daddy [INAUDIBLE] after night shift, I tried to walk to [INAUDIBLE], to get some little small-- they allow on the small portion of bread, which I went by foot, and I-- as delicate as I was supposed to be, but somehow was strong then.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I sent for my daddy that sent a small package, because [INAUDIBLE] to walk that far.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Daddy used to get those little packages.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, shortly when I was there, so I didn't want to go to the office, like after I was-- I regretted, because they had their own room, they had double, double, everything double.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't know then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And no dirty work, just everything clean.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was naive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't-- but who knew about what to do?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I thought I do a great thing, go to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I was in the kitchen, the German head of the camp, he made an appel, and again he chose me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I got scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said, to the Jew-- to the German kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was two German woman they used to come every day on the bicycle to help out, some peeling potatoes, whatever they need for the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was privileged to go to this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Meantime, when I-- one day I-- trying to get some hot water, I scald my whole leg, from here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I tore off the stocking, with-- but-- and the whole skin, I think, it took-- you know, it took off with it, and it was horrible.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in terrible pain, and I couldn't walk, naturally.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And usually they send right away all sick people, or couldn't-- if they couldn't work, they weren't no use for them.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
